name: Eros&Thanatos
description: This NFT is forever connected with physical oil painting dimm.60x50 cm, made in Warsaw, Poland by me - Dominik Jalowinski in 2020. If You buy it I'm going to deliver this painting to You at my cost. So should do every new owner in case of further sales. This painting as well as it's digital, animated  version and lenticular print based on this painting was presented at exhibition "Void Connoisseur" in WIDNA Gallery during Cracow Art Week https://cracowartweek.pl/void-connoisseur/ on june 2021. There is also a virtual version of exhibition on https://www.cryptovoxels.com/s/widna You can see my other works on IG @dj_alowinski
